{"tid":623741,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★4-10 小心！美國政府今晚隨時「震散」金融市場","createTime":"2018-04-10T08:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T16:53:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"259c7d340ad7cdaf2df5323cf90c876ce7218106","tid":623741,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"港股收市後，今晚外圍的重點不是經濟數據，而是美國政府，他們的行動隨時惹起金融市場大幅波動！<br />\n<br />\n今晚的「大事」分別是社交媒體Facebook創辦人朱克伯格將會出席國會聽證會，就數據外洩作證；美國白宮勢會短期內宣布敘利亞軍事行動，以回應該國使用化學武器發動襲擊，一旦落實，油價必定大幅上落；總統特朗普「通俄門」事件仍在調查當中，隨時再爆出新證據；<span style=\"color: red;\">又或者特朗普再「發神經」，對中國貿易祭出新方案。</span><br />\n<br />\n故此，今晚金融市場的「震央」是以特朗普為首的美國政府<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180410/bkn-20180410161541705-0410_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180410%2Fbkn-20180410161541705-0410_00842_001.html&d=5v%2FDwfTm9hZZ%2BvngnM%2Ffv%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0dd11f5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180410/bkn-20180410161541705-0410_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8e3b81121367d1ebd4ead597b817644536daf44b","tid":623741,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"drop 2000 tmr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53279d5f50e220e4d4667d7fb7ef233a7a3c6ece","tid":623741,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"又或者特朗普再「發神經」<br />\n又或者特朗普再「發神經」<br />\n又或者特朗普再「發神經」<br />\n又或者特朗普再「發神經」"},{"pid":"9f30579a1cd0f757eb80d3c8d050c6171b474b6c","tid":623741,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> y u here"},{"pid":"44